/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `«expr⊥» -/
/-- The trivial pretopology induces the trivial grothendieck topology. -/
theorem to_grothendieck_bot : toGrothendieck C («expr⊥») = «expr⊥» :=
  (gi C).gc.l_bot
#align to_grothendieck_bot to_grothendieck_bot
mem_to_grothendieck:
theorem mem_to_grothendieck (K : Pretopology C) (X S) : S ∈ toGrothendieck C K X ↔ ∃ R ∈ K X, R ≤ (S : Presieve X) :=
  iff.rfl
#align mem_to_grothendieck mem_to_grothendieck
